{"tid":2021611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"這條水壩不止會搞到下游的泰國人沒水，連帶還會搞到東南亞斷糧，香港會饑荒。","createTime":"2020-05-17T23:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T17:46:44.000Z","uid":40147,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd4c8a55c71a37ab387daf8bdae07dc41d62dae","tid":2021611,"uid":40147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:48:34.000Z","msg":"上次湄公河的聯署不達標失敗了，於是出了ver2。<br />\n希望這次可以早一點開始推。<br />\n這條水壩不止會搞到下游的泰國人沒水，連帶還會搞到東南亞斷糧，香港會饑荒。<br />\n（特別提一下，其實這也跟馬來西亞有關，因爲全球糧食供應會下降，糧食價格會上升）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river-0?fbclid=IwAR0LhUXH7Fdc5a1h9RokyfiBHjI6dsQd44hI9guCHl6XKBqmHBt8DevShuE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river-0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0LhUXH7Fdc5a1h9RokyfiBHjI6dsQd44hI9guCHl6XKBqmHBt8DevShuE&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=eabb1fd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river-0?fbclid=IwAR0LhUXH7Fdc5a1h9RokyfiBHjI6dsQd44hI9guCHl6XKBqmHBt8DevShuE</a><br />\n一樣，幫簽幫分享啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaed42a4adbf1700ac0d594404b8d8d95db83dc","tid":2021611,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0706b647e67eab0a784fdae0d81bd6d3af71589","tid":2021611,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:14:36.000Z","msg":"Signed"},{"pid":"a7e46c279f9e0c20fcc03f90c2233a889b930d90","tid":2021611,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:16:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d27d2f094d270602c52a84c4b2492d6e710f94b","tid":2021611,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"